 "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1629391393", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 180843, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393", "stars": 3398, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 279788, "username": "crack105", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/crack105", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a3f0/4c8f/279788_mini.png?m=1635667621", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a3f0/4c8f/279788_normal.png?m=1635667621", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a3f0/4c8f/279788_large.png?m=1635667621", "created": 1515074333, "last_modified": 1635667621}, "last_reply_by": "germain", "last_touched": 1642512684, "title": "有哪些相对保值的爱好？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/828859", "created": 1642429238, "deleted": 0, "content": "先说说自己觉得比较保值的爱好吧，摄影和 CSGO\r\n摄影：入坑摄影，海鲜市场摄影器材买买卖卖，玩了一年半换了好几个镜头机身，总亏损不超过两三百\r\nCSGO：饰品(皮肤) 可 RMB 自由交易，部分饰品时间越久越保值，现在卖掉还能赚个几百甚至几千，并且可以提现", "content_rendered": "先说说自己觉得比较保值的爱好吧，摄影和 CSGO<br />摄影：入坑摄影，海鲜市场摄影器材买买卖卖，玩了一年半换了好几个镜头机身，总亏损不超过两三百<br />CSGO：饰品(皮肤) 可 RMB 自由交易，部分饰品时间越久越保值，现在卖掉还能赚个几百甚至几千，并且可以提现", "last_modified": 1642429238, "replies": 90, "id": 828859}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1629391393", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1629391393", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 180843, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393", "stars": 3398, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 433612, "username": "stormer", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/stormer", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/eb22b924f30a344cfdc57e33bb1a2470?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/eb22b924f30a344cfdc57e33bb1a2470?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/eb22b924f30a344cfdc57e33bb1a2470?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1564748363, "last_modified": 1642487253}, "last_reply_by": "treblex", "last_touched": 1642512122, "title": "区块链就是: 手上拿着锤子，看啥都想锤两下? 除了发币到底还能解决什么问题?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/829011", "created": 1642491108, "deleted": 0, "content": "看到这个 https://v2ex.com/t/828968 勾起了我一直以来都有的困惑\r\n\r\n麻烦大家给解解惑\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n- **所谓的联盟链** 仅仅是几家公司的服务器组成的网络,数据又不公开,还能改链上的数据,那这个跟每家公司自己单独放个数据库,再开个接收发送的 api 有什么区别? 也没见到解决了什么信任问题啊? 这 api 接口照样能校验数据,拒绝不合法数据吧? 再不行每条数据加个 hash(上条数据的 hash+本条数据) 不就行了?\r\n- **所谓的私有链** 这个就是文本数据库吧? 查询没数据库快,速度还比数据库慢,到底解决了什么问题?\r\n- 什么产品溯源,毕业证溯源,防伪的,怎么解决源头造假? 怎么解决数据录入人造假问题? 一般这种都私有链,那上链的数据不还随便改? 如果开放外部节点加入,没有奖励又有谁愿意提供计算资源?\r\n- 如果是公有链应用,那就是大家都能往链上存数据,那就无法审查数据了?\r\n\r\n所以,区块链是不是只适合发币?", "content_rendered": "<p>看到这个 <a href=\"https://v2ex.com/t/828968\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://v2ex.com/t/828968</a> 勾起了我一直以来都有的困惑</p>\n<p>麻烦大家给解解惑</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>所谓的联盟链</strong> 仅仅是几家公司的服务器组成的网络,数据又不公开,还能改链上的数据,那这个跟每家公司自己单独放个数据库,再开个接收发送的 api 有什么区别? 也没见到解决了什么信任问题啊? 这 api 接口照样能校验数据,拒绝不合法数据吧? 再不行每条数据加个 hash(上条数据的 hash+本条数据) 不就行了?</li>\n<li><strong>所谓的私有链</strong> 这个就是文本数据库吧? 查询没数据库快,速度还比数据库慢,到底解决了什么问题?</li>\n<li>什么产品溯源,毕业证溯源,防伪的,怎么解决源头造假? 怎么解决数据录入人造假问题? 一般这种都私有链,那上链的数据不还随便改? 如果开放外部节点加入,没有奖励又有谁愿意提供计算资源?</li>\n<li>如果是公有链应用,那就是大家都能往链上存数据,那就无法审查数据了?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>所以,区块链是不是只适合发币?</p>\n", "last_modified": 1642491108, "replies": 72, "id": 829011}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_large.png?m=1611920927", "name": "games", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_normal.png?m=1611920927", "title": "游戏", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/games", "topics": 2115, "footer": "", "header": "Life is short, have more fun.", "title_alternative": "Games", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_mini.png?m=1611920927", "stars": 1943, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 55, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 434804, "username": "Zhancha", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Zhancha", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50e6/b547/434804_mini.png?m=1565341086", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50e6/b547/434804_normal.png?m=1565341086", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/50e6/b547/434804_large.png?m=1565341086", "created": 1565340792, "last_modified": 1565341086}, "last_reply_by": "jtshs256", "last_touched": 1642509315, "title": "想玩点主机游戏，求推荐。", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/828894", "created": 1642464929, "deleted": 0, "content": "之前不怎么打游戏，只玩过 LOL ，魔兽争霸。\r\n\r\n也没买过 Switch ，PS 等主机，可能以后（几年后）等有钱了再买。\r\n\r\n现在想大家推荐几个能在电脑上玩的游戏，例如 Steam 平台的游戏等等。\r\n\r\n感谢大伙。", "content_rendered": "<p>之前不怎么打游戏，只玩过 LOL ，魔兽争霸。</p>\n<p>也没买过 Switch ，PS 等主机，可能以后（几年后）等有钱了再买。</p>\n<p>现在想大家推荐几个能在电脑上玩的游戏，例如 Steam 平台的游戏等等。</p>\n<p>感谢大伙。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1642464929, "replies": 70, "id": 828894}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1641783557", "name": "windows", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1641783557", "title": "Windows", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows", "topics": 2511, "footer": "", "header": "Windows, not walls.", "title_alternative": "Windows", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1641783557", "stars": 824, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 144066, "username": "mikeven", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/mikeve